  PreLevelDialogue:
  - "Kid, it\u2019s time. After that performance, I think it\u2019s time. Time to
    make some MONEY!!"
  - "Cha-Ching! Can you hear it? It\u2019s the sound of counting machines! Very close
    counting machines."
  - "Do you want to know why? BECAUSE ol\u2019 Bill has a job for you!"
  - Mhm, no need to thank me! I found some rich schmuck.. I mean some well-off admirer
    of art, who LOVES the sound of your traditional sculpting methods.
  - "Willing to pay some good money too. Naturally, we\u2019ll split it 50/50, right?"
  - "Okay okay, I can settle with 65/35, just don\u2019t go forgetting me when you\u2019re
    famous!"
  - 'Okay, the order has just come through, are you ready? Go on, get to it! '
